(32, 'faq_display', '[{\"title\": \"What is an ERP system?\",\"description\": \"An ERP (Enterprise Resource Planning) system is a software platform that integrates various business processes and functions into a unified system. It helps organizations manage their operations more efficiently by providing real-time data and insights across different departments.\"},{\"title\": \"How can an ERP system benefit my business?\",\"description\": \"An ERP system can streamline business processes, improve data accuracy, enhance collaboration between departments, and provide valuable insights for decision-making. It can help reduce operational costs, increase productivity, and improve overall business performance.\"},{\"title\": \"Is your ERP system customizable?\",\"description\": \"Yes, our ERP system is highly customizable. You can tailor it to meet the specific needs of your business by configuring modules, workflows, and reports. We also offer custom development services for more specialized requirements.\"},{\"title\": \"What kind of support do you offer for your ERP system?\",\"description\": \"We offer comprehensive support for our ERP system, including 24/7 technical support, detailed documentation, and training programs. Our support team is dedicated to helping you resolve any issues and make the most of our software.\"},{\"title\": \"How secure is your ERP system?\",\"description\": \"Security is a top priority for us. Our ERP system includes robust security features such as user authentication, role-based access control, data encryption, and audit logs to protect your data and ensure compliance with industry standards.\"}]', '2024-06-08 05:56:20', '2024-06-08 05:56:20'),
